dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Dark Hole quadrangle, Monterey, Fresno & Kings Counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle THE DARK HOLE, CA 1961, DMA 1955 IV NE -- Series V895, REVISED 1993."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
